# Bootstrap Template — Test Infrastructure Setup

When `tests/` directory does not exist, create this structure before generating any test code.

## Directory Structure

```
tests/
├── CMakeLists.txt          # Main test build file
├── CMakePresets.json        # Test configure/build/test presets
├── unit/                    # Test source files
│   └── test_<module>.c
├── fakes/                   # fff fake headers
│   └── fake_<driver>.h
├── stubs/                   # x86 stub sources (.c files for link-time substitution)
│   ├── CMSIS/               # ARM CMSIS header stubs
│   │   ├── arm_math.h
│   │   ├── core_cm4.h
│   │   └── core_cmFunc.h
│   └── mcu/                 # MCU-specific header stubs
│       ├── {{mcu}}.h
│       └── define.h
└── support/                 # Test-only support headers and configs
    └── test_config.h
```

